At this checkpoint:
- Created a build_index.rb script to create a json-based index from the Getty data.
- Created a sub-directory in bin/, called lunr_index.

- Implemented two search scripts: search.js, which builds the lunr index on the fly and runs a simple trial search, and quick_search.js, which used the pre-built index and runs a simple trial search.

When I get back, I'll incorporate these into the website.
